I will moreover that they hold all that is above written, as freely and quietly as 1 hold my own lands3 and I will that the Abbot hold his court as freely, fully, and honourably, as the Bishop of Saint Andrews, and the Abbot of Dunsermline, and the Abbot of Kelso hold their eourts.
